title: Good2Go Auto Insurance website provides the fastest quotes online
text:
Good2Go
ATLANTA , Aug. 26, Good2Go®, specialists in offering minimum coverage auto insurance, was recently found to provide drivers the fastest auto insurance Quote: on the Internet.
In fact, when tested by independent third parties, Good2Go® provided a Quote: in 59 seconds and outperformed all of the top ten auto insurance carriers in the country including Progressive and Allstate. Even GEICO, their closest competitor, was more than two times slower than Good2Go.com.
"We're extremely proud our website is the fastest on the Internet when it comes to providing drivers the car insurance Quote: s they need," says Joe DeLago , CEO of Good2Go®, "but most of all, we look forward to providing drivers the coverage they need to get on the road again quickly and safely."
About Good2Go®: Based in Atlanta, GA , Good2Go® is a member of American Independent Companies, which offers affordable car insurance online to help uninsured drivers get the car insurance they need to drive legally. Good2Go® specializes in minimum liability car insurance, and also offers collision and comprehensive coverage. For more information, visit good2go.com
